data.title: nice stuff
data.text: Truly saying I ordered delivery to hotel, but delivery could be faster. From other side pizza wasn't cold, but like just from oven. So no complaints.

data.title: The pizzas were delicious.
data.text: I am thankful that the 4 pizzas were delivered while they were still warm. but it took a long time for them to get here.  There was a delivery fee attached to each pizza, which I didn't understand---since they were all delivered at the same time.  I always tell the delivery driver to keep the change, so this extra delivery fee is cutting into his tip.
